                    h2 YASB for X-Wing 2.0 Legacy
                :markdown
                    YASB 2.0 is a simple, fast, no-frills squad builder for [X-Wing Miniatures](http://www.fantasyflightgames.com/edge_minisite.asp?eidm=174&enmi=X-Wing) by [Fantasy Flight Games](http://www.fantasyflightgames.com/index.asp).

                    It is pure HTML, JavaScript, and CSS and requires no backend, and can be dropped into place on any website (with maybe a few CSS tweaks).

                    YASB for X-wing 2.0 Legacy is a community fork of [YASB 2.5](https://yasb.app).
                    You can give your feedback here : [X-wing 2.0 Discord Server](https://discord.com/invite/gnU2CKVGYv)
                    Updated rules and information can be found here : [Infinite Arenas 2.0 Legacy](https://infinitearenas.com/legacy/docs)

                    YASB 2.5 is updated and maintained by Stephen Kim.

                    2.0 launch data thanks to Evan Cameron, Jonathan Hon, Devon Monkhouse, and Mark Stewart.
                    
                    Translation Team: Patrick Mischke, godgremos, ClÃ©ment Bourgoin, ManuelWittke

